{"tid":2503961,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"嚴選華語樂壇三大擁有最多最惡戰狼fans 嘅歌手 網驚千萬不能得罪","createTime":"2021-04-25T13:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T04:19:37.000Z","uid":27915,"like":4,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9bf6a23db0b37fd369c4bffb378a298cf0238137","tid":2503961,"uid":27915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T13:15:59.000Z","msg":"排名分先後，只針對fans不針對歌手本人<br />\n<br />\n3 蔡依林<br />\n19年金曲奬華語專輯同女歌手先後輸俾 孫盛希、林憶蓮 搞到金曲獎live留言狂屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好在後尾攞返年度歌曲同年度專輯，唔係真係台灣暴動。仲要當屆評審團陳珊妮喺20年前 評價過 蔡依林係 十大爛歌手，多年積怨再度引爆。<br />\n<br />\n2 林家謙<br />\n由上年輸咗哭喪，到攞完呢幾日連登情況，自己有眼見。大大力情緒勒索，屌林家謙= 謀殺樂壇。唔俾人覺得唔好聽、唔接受其他意見批評，只准表揚。仲要自把自為幫林家謙解釋，林真係多得班fans唔少。<br />\n<br />\n1 五月天<br />\n有人想知再講"},{"pid":"7deebd41487addc5f90557f3dfeb8ff39dce502a","tid":2503961,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T13:17:31.000Z","msg":"eason呢"},{"pid":"4d0cb95dc294216265849e39a222bce8c1b755a6","tid":2503961,"uid":32657,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"7deebd41487addc5f90557f3dfeb8ff39dce502a","tid":2503961,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T13:17:31.000Z","msg":"eason呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-25T13:17:41.000Z","msg":"會員編號：#228143<p class=\"left\"> </p>會員名稱：係！各位網友！ <p class=\"left\"> </p>註冊日期：2018/12/24<p class=\"left\"> </p><blockquote> </blockquote><a href=\"https://bit.ly/lihkg_on9_list\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Flihkg_on9_list&d=41Q62glp5DA2hxteu4KnmbTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=6268fcd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/lihkg_on9_list</a><blockquote> </blockquote><p class=\"left\"> </p><p class=\"left\"> </p>小心此人 <span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">⚠️</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><p class=\"left\"> </p><span class=\"violet\">踩本土煮食 youtuber，喪推支那王剛，稱「睇王剛啦 有新辦公室 就搞掂好認真 正正經經睇王剛啦 」。</span><p class=\"left\"> <